@startuml class_prescription
' ============================================================
' Class Diagram: Prescription Service (Cart)
' ============================================================
skinparam classBackgroundColor #AEE2F0
skinparam classBorderColor #0D47A1
skinparam classHeaderBackgroundColor #0D47A1
skinparam classHeaderFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classFontSize 12
skinparam classAttributeFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor #0D47A1
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

package"prescription-service :8004 (FastAPI · prescription_db)"#E3F2FD {

  class Prescription {
    <<ORM Persistable · Aggregate Root>>
    -ID : String (UUID)
    -customer_id : String
    -prescription_status : String
    -cart_status : String
    -subtotal : Decimal
    -total_amount : Decimal
    -currency : String
    -issued_date : DateTime
    -valid_until : Date
    -max_refills : int
    -created_at : DateTime
    -fulfilled_date : DateTime
    -notes : String
  }

  class PrescriberInfo {
    <<ORM Persistable · Value Object>>
    -ID : int
    -prescription_id : String
    -name : String
    -license_number : String
    -specialty : String
    -hospital : String
  }

  class Diagnosis {
    <<ORM Persistable>>
    -ID : int
    -prescription_id : String
    -icd10_code : String
    -condition_name : String
    -notes : String
  }

  class PrescriptionItem {
    <<ORM Persistable>>
    -ID : int
    -prescription_id : String
    -product_id : String
    -sku : String
    -product_name : String
    -quantity : int
    -unit_price : Decimal
    -currency : String
    -requires_prescription : bool
    -frequency : String
    -duration : String
    -dosage : String
    -fulfill_quantity : int
  }
}

note right of Prescription
  Đóng vai trò là **Cart Service**
  trong mẫu E-Commerce.
  customer_id = account_id từ api-gateway.
  Bị xóa sau khi dispensing-service
  tạo Order thành công.
end note

note bottom of PrescriptionItem
  product_id → tham chiếu cross-service
  đến pharmacy-service Product
end note

Prescription *--"1"PrescriberInfo
Prescription *--"0..*"Diagnosis
Prescription *--"1..*"PrescriptionItem

@enduml
